Lore.AirJump.1=Leru's gift, to cut through the air, proved instumental in aiding Ori with their quest. This {$Mods.OriMod.Common.Medal} was a manifestation of such a gift.
Lore.AirJump.2=In the months following the beginning of Nibel's Blindness, Leru found a key that sealed the Ginso Tree, and with it, possibly the way to saving Nibel.
Lore.AirJump.3=Gumo had stolen the Water Vein from Leru. Without it, she could not enter the Ginso tree, the path to saving Nibel from Decay.
Lore.AirJump.4=Leru had understood. Despite her determination, she simply lacked the strength to face Ginso's malaise. Even Reem, certainly more capable than Leru, has fallen to it already.

