ItemName.BashLevel2=Enhanced Bash {$Mods.OriMod.Common.Medal}
ItemName.BashLevel3=Ultra Bash {$Mods.OriMod.Common.Medal}

ItemTooltip.BashLevel1=Allows you to Bash on enemies and projectiles, launching you in one direction and the target in the opposite direction.
ItemTooltip.BashLevel2=Enhances your Bashing capabilities to target projectiles, and deal damage to NPCs.
ItemTooltip.BashLevel3=Greatly enhances your Bashing speeds, distance, and damage dealt.

Lore.Bash.1=When the Ginso Tree's waters turned poisonous, Reem tried to help, but he could not predict just how bad the Decay would be when Nibel went blind. This {$Mods.OriMod.Common.Medal} was a manifestation of his legacy.
Lore.Bash.2=Reem quickly learned the issues plaguing Nibel, and possible solutions to the Blindness. He rushed alone, determined to fix the issue as soon as possible. This, however, proved unwise.
Lore.Bash.3=Decay was a vicious force, Reem was forced to learn in her attempts in saving Nibel. That knowledge was left to rot in her Ancestral Tree, deep within the Ginso Tree.

