ItemName.StompLevel2=Ultra Stomp {$Mods.OriMod.Common.Medal}

ItemTooltip.StompLevel1=Allows you to slam into the ground, creating a powerful shockwave to damage nearby enemies.
ItemTooltip.StompLevel2=Enhances your stomping capabilities for even more damage, pushing enemies far back.

Lore.Stomp.1=Despite being known as the strongest of Nibel's Spirits, Ilo was a gentle Spirit. Still, his strength knew no bounds. This {$Mods.OriMod.Common.Medal} was a manifestation of his power.
Lore.Stomp.2=Ilo gave it his all to protect the land of Nibel; however, no Spirit could survive Kuro's wrath...

